Diamond::
She made sure they all got a room. Then she opened her link. "KitKat, 
They are ready to see you now."

::KitKat:: 
"Great, I'll be right there." She walked out of the conference room 
and went down the corridor. She found Diamond in the hall. "Good. 
They're all settled in and comfortable. Which one is the leader?"

Diamond::
She pointed to Killfest's room. "He's in there."

KitKat::
"Excelent. Thank you for all your help Diamond. You've been a big 
help."  She turned and walked to Killfest's room. She knocked on the 
door. "Hello? I'm KitKat, leader of the predacons. You said you 
wanted to talk, so let's talk." she said with a smile on her face and 
standing outside at the room door.
